ENTLY VERIFIED SECURITY\nSecurity is not a claim. It is validated.\n• Validated under NIST's Cryptographic Algorithm Validation Program (CAVP)\n• Publicly listed on the official NIST website\n• Independently audited and certified by DEKRA\n• AES-256 encryption\n• End-to-end encrypted messages, calls, and file transfers\nMessages are encrypted on your device before transmission and can only be decrypted by the intended recipient.\n\nADVANCED PRIVACY CONTROLS\n• Tools to manage and delete conversations across devices\n• Options to remove communication history when needed\n• Ability to protect your data if a device is lost or replaced\n• Chats can be configured to only be accessible while connected to the internet\n\nFlicker™ Mode: Disappearing messages from 30 seconds to 24 hours.\nPhoto & Video Distiller™ automatically removes metadata before encryption.\n\nMORE THAN JUST SECURE MESSAGING\n• Secure one-to-one and group messaging\n• Encrypted voice and video calls\n• Integration with Xave® encrypted vault\n• Desktop and web access\n\nPrivacy is not a feature. It is a right.\n\nTerms of Use: https://xpal.com/terms  \n\nPrivacy Policy: https://xpal.com/privacy-policy","rating":4.7,"ratingCount":"121","buttonAction":{"title":"Get","presentationStyle":[],"actionMetrics":{"$kind":"ActionMetrics","data":[{"fields":{"reco_algoId":"cab_1","reco_eligible":"1","reco_hash":"cab_1","actionDetails":{"buyParams":"productType=C&price=0&salableAdamId=1536908440&pricingParameters=STDQ&pg=default&appExtVrsId=884931324"},"location":[{"locationPosition":0,"locationType":"button","name":"Get","reco_algoId":"cab_1","reco_eligible":"1","reco_hash":"cab_1","idType":"its_id","id":"1536908440"},{"locationPosition":3,"locationType":"lockup","name":"xPal Ultra Secure Messenger","reco_algoId":"cab_1","reco_eligible":"1","reco_hash":"cab_1","idType":"its_id","id":"1536908440"},{"locationPosition":7,"locationType":"similarItems","name":"You Might Also Like","idType":"relationship","id":"customers-a